HEADWORD: Professionalism
<hw>Pro*fes"sion*al*ism</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The
following of a profession, sport, etc., as an occupation; -- opposed to
<ant>amateurism</ant>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

